        <trans-unit id="101" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Describes the timing of binding source updates.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="102" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve" extradata="MT">
          <source>For more information, see &lt;xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.UpdateSourceTrigger%2A?displayProperty=fullName&gt;.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="103" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The default UpdateSourceTrigger value of the binding target property.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="104" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The default value for most dependency properties is PropertyChanged, while the &lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox.Text*&gt; property has a default value of LostFocus.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="105" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve" extradata="MT">
          <source>A programmatic way to determine the default &lt;xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.UpdateSourceTrigger%2A&gt; value of a dependency property is to get the property metadata of the property using &lt;xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.GetMetadata%2A&gt; and then check the value of the &lt;xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.DefaultUpdateSourceTrigger%2A&gt; property.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="106" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>To be added.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="107" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Updates the binding source only when you call the &lt;xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression.UpdateSource*&gt; method.</source>
